                   dreamed of owning an exotic fresh or salt- 
                   water fish tank for your home, but the cost 
                   and maintenance was just too much? 

                   Your dream has come true! AquaZone is the 
                   desktop garden that delivers a state-of- 
                   the-art digital aquarium for your PC! 

                   An aquarium so vibrant, so life-like, you will 
                   swear the fish are real!

                   aquatic wildlife!


                   - 20 different species of fresh or saltwater 
                     fish! 
                   - 8 different tanks - each with unique plantlife

                     can handle!

                      watch you 
                   - Fish cam - closely follow your favorite fish 
                     friends 
                   - Soothing sound effects 
                   - Your choice of 8 photorealistic backgrounds 
                   - Wireframe, fully rendered, or silhouette mode
